quran[431]{c,v,t}:
  67,1,"Nihayat buzurg-o-bartar hai woh jiske haath mein qayinaat ki sultanat hai , aur woh har cheez par qudrat rakhta hai"
  67,2,"Jisne maut aur zindagi ko ijaat kiya taa-ke tum logon ko aazma kar dekhey tum mein se kaun behtar amal karne wala hai, aur woh zabardast bhi hai aur darguzar farmane wala bhi"
  67,3,"Jisne teh-bar-teh saat (seven) aasman banaye tum Rehman ki takhleeq(creation) mein kisi kism ki be-rabti (incongruity) na paogey phir palat kar dekho, kahin tumhein koi khalal (flaw) nazar aata hai"
  67,4,Baar baar nigaah daudao tumhari nigaah thak kar na-murad palat aayegi
  67,5,Humne tumhare kareeb ke aasman ko azeem-o-shaan chiragon se aarasta (adorned /beautify) kiya hai aur unhein shayateen ko maar bhagane ka zariya bana diya hai. In shaytano ke liye bhadakti hui aag humne muhayya kar rakkhi hai
  67,6,Jin logon ne apne Rubb se kufr kiya hai unke liye jahannum ka azaab hai aur woh bahut hi bura thikana hai
  67,7,Jab woh usmein phenke jayenge to uske dhahadne (roar) ki haulnaak aawaz sunengey aur woh josh kha rahi hogi
  67,8,"Shiddat-e-gazab se phati jati hogi, har baar jab koi anbwah (multitude/group) us mein dala jayega uske kaarinde (keepers) un logon se puchenge “kya tumhare paas koi khabardaar karne wala nahin aaya tha?”"
  67,9,"Woh jawab denge “haan ,khabardaar karne wala hamare paas aaya tha,magar humne usey jhutla diya aur kaha Allah ne kuch bhi nazil nahin kiya hai, tum badi gumraahi mein padey huey ho”"
  67,10,Aur woh kahenge “kaash hum sunte ya samajhte to aaj is bhadakti hui aag ke sazawaron mein na shamil hotey”
  67,11,"Is tarah woh apne kasoor ka khud aitraaf (confess) kar lengey, laanat hai in dozakhiyon par"
  67,12,"Jo log be-dekhe apne Rubb se darte hai , yaqeenan unke liye magfirat hai aur bada ajar"
  67,13,Tum khwah chupke se baat karo ya unchi aawaz se (Allah ke liye yaksa hai) woh to dilon ka haal tak jaanta hai
  67,14,Kya wahi na jaanega jisne paida kiya hai? Halanke woh baareek-been aur bakhabar hai
  67,15,"Wahi to hai jisne tumhare liye zameen ko taabeh kar rakkha hai , chalo uski chaati par aur khao khuda ka rizq, usi ke huzoor tumhein dobara zinda ho kar jana hai"
  67,16,Kya tum issey be-khauf ho ke woh jo aasman mein hai tumhein zameen mein dhasa de aur yakayak yeh zameen jhakoley khane lagey (shake/rock violently)
  67,17,Kya tum issey be-khauf ho ke wo jo aasman mein hai tum par pathrao karne wali hawa bhej de? Phir tumhein maloom ho jayega ke meri tambeeh (warning) kaisi hoti hai
  67,18,Inse pehle guzre huey log jhutla chuke hain phir dekhlo ke meri giraft kaisi sakht thi
  67,19,Kya yeh log apne upar udney waley parindon ko par phaylaye aur sukedte nahin dekhte? Rehman ke siwa koi nahin jo inhein thamey huey ho. Wahi har cheez ka nigehbaan hai
  67,20,"Batao, aakhir woh kaunsa lashkar tumhare paas hai jo Rehman ke muqable mein tumhari madad kar sakta hai? Haqeeqat yeh hai ke yeh mukireen dhoke mein padey huey hain"
  67,21,"Ya phir batao, kaun hai jo tumhein rizq de sakta hai agar Rehman apna rizq roak ley? Dar-asal yeh log sarkashi aur haqq se gurez par adey huey hai"
  67,22,"Bhala socho, jo shaks mooh aundhaey (grovelling) chal raha ho woh zyada sahih raah paney wala hai ya woh jo sar uthaye seedha ek hamwar sadak par chal raha ho"
  67,23,"Inse kaho Allah hi hai jisne tumhein paida kiya, tumko sunney aur dekhne ki taaqatein di aur sochne samajhne waley dil diye, magar tum kam hi shukr ada karte ho"
  67,24,"Insey kaho, Allah hi hai jisne tumhein zameen mein phailaya hai aur usi ki taraf tum sametey jaogey"
  67,25,Yeh kehte hain “Agar tum sacchey ho to batao yeh wada kab poora hoga?”
  67,26,"Kaho “Iska ilm to Allah ke paas hai, main to bas saaf saaf khabardar kardene wala hoon"
  67,27,"Phir jab yeh us cheez ko kareeb dekh lenge to un sab logon ke chehre bigad jayenge jinhon ne inkar kiya hai, aur us waqt unse kaha jayega ke yahi hai woh cheez jiske liye tum takazey kar rahey (ask for) thay"
  67,28,"Insey kaho, kabhi tumne yeh bhi socha ke Allah khwa mujhey aur mere saathiyon ko halaaq karde ya hum par Reham karey, kafiron ko dardnaak azaab se kaun bacha lega"
  67,29,"Insey kaho, woh bada Raheem hai, usi par hum imaan laye hain, aur usi par hamara bharosa hai, ankareeb tumhein maloom ho jayega ke sareeh gumrahi (manifest error) mein pada hua kaun hai"
  67,30,"Inse kaho, kabhi tumne yeh bhi socha ke agar tumhare kuwon (wells) ka pani zameen mein utar jaye to kaun hai jo is pani ki behti hui sotein (flowing water) tumhein nikal kar la dega"
  68,1,"Noon, Kasam hai qalam ki aur us cheez ki jisey likhne waley likh rahey hain"
  68,2,Tum apne Rubb ke fazl se majnoon (deewane) nahin ho
  68,3,Aur yaqeenan tumhare liye aisa ajar (reward) hai jiska silsila kabhi khatm honay wala nahin
  68,4,Aur beshak tum akhlaaq ke bade martabe par ho
  68,5,Anqareeb tum bhi dekh logey aur woh bhi dekh lenge
  68,6,Ke tum mein se kaun junoon (madness) mein mubtala hai
  68,7,"Tumhara Rubb un logon ko bhi khoob jaanta hai jo uski raah se bhatkey huey hain , aur wahi unko bhi acchi tarah jaanta hai jo raah-e-raast par hai"
  68,8,Lihaza tum in jhutlane walon ke dabao mein hargiz na aao
  68,9,yeh to chahte hain ke kuch tum mudahnat (narmi) karo to yeh bhi mudahnat (narmi) karein
  68,10,Hargiz na dabo kisi aisey shaks se jo bahut kasmein khane wala be-waqaat (worthless) aadmi hai
  68,11,"Taaney deta hai , chugliyan khata phirta hai (slanderer, gossip-monger)"
  68,12,"Bhalayi se rokta hai , zulm-o-zyadti mein hadd se guzar janey wala hai, sakht badh-amal hai , jafa-kaar hai"
  68,13,Aur in sab uyub (aib) ke saath badh-asl (illegitimate child) hai
  68,14,Is bina par ke woh bahut maal-o-aulad rakhta hai
  68,15,Jab hamari aayat usko sunayi jati hai to kehta hai yeh to agle waqton ke afsane hain
  68,16,Ankareeb hum iski sund (snout) par daag lagayenge
  68,17,"Humne in (ehle makkah) ko usi taraah aazmaish mein dala hai jis tarah ek baagh (garden) ke maalikon ko aazmaish mein dala tha, jab unhon ne kasam khayi ke subah sawerey zaroor apne baagh ke phal todenge"
  68,18,Aur woh koi istasna (exception) nahin kar rahey thay
  68,19,Raat ko woh soye padey thay ke tumhare Rubb ki taraf se ek balaa is baagh par phir gayi
  68,20,Aur uska haal aisa ho gaya jaise kati hui fasal ho
  68,21,Subah un logon ne ek dusre ko pukara
  68,22,Kaha agar phal todne hai ho to sawerey sawerey apni kheti ki taraf nikal chalo
  68,23,Chunanchey woh chal padey aur aapas mein chupke chupke kehte jatay thay
  68,24,Ke aaj koi miskeen tumhare paas baag mein na aane paye
  68,25,Woh kuch na dene ka faisla kiye huye subah sawerey jaldi jaldi is tarah wahan gaye jaise ke woh (phal todne par) qadir hain
  68,26,Magar jab baagh ko dekha to kehne lagey “hum raasta bhool gaye hain
  68,27,Nahin balke hum mehroom reh gaye”
  68,28,Un mein jo sab se behtar aadmi tha usne kaha “maine tumse kaha na tha ke tum tasbeeh kyun nahin karte?”
  68,29,"Woh pukar utthey paak hai hamara Rubb, waqayi hum gunahgaar thay"
  68,30,Phir unmein se har ek dusre ko malamat karne laga
  68,31,"Akhir ko unhon ne kaha “afsos hamare haal par, beshak hum sarkash ho gaye thay"
  68,32,"Baeed (door) nahin ke hamara Rubb humein badle mein issey behtar baagh ata farmaye, hum apne Rubb ki taraf rujoo karte hain"
  68,33,"Aisa hota hai azaab aur aakhirat ka azaab issey bhi bada hai, kaash yeh log isko jaante"
  68,34,Yaqeenan khuda-tars logon ke liye unke Rubb ke yahan niyamat bhari jannatein hain
  68,35,Kya hum farma-bardaaron ka haal mujreemon sa kardein
  68,36,"Tum logon ko kya ho gaya hai, tum kaise hukum lagate ho"
  68,37,Kya tumhare paas koi kitaab hai jismein tum yeh padhte ho
  68,38,Ke tumhare liye zaroor wahan wahi kuch hai jo tum apne liye pasand karte ho
  68,39,Ya phir kya tumhare liye roz-e-qayamat tak humpar kuch ahad-o-paiman (covenant) sabit hai ke tumhein wahi kuch milega jiska tum hukum lagao
  68,40,Inse pucho tum mein se kaun iska zaamin (gurantee/responsible) hai
  68,41,Ya phir inke thehraye huye kuch sahreek hain (jinhon ne iska zimma liya ho)?yeh baat hai to layein apne shareekon ko agar yeh sacchey hain
  68,42,Jis roz sakht waqt aa padega aur logon ko sajda karne ke liye bulaya jayega to yeh log sajda na kar sakenge
  68,43,"Inki nigaahein nichey hongi, zillat inpar chaa rahi hogi. Yeh jab sahi-o-saalim thay us waqt inhein sajde ke liye (bulaya jata tha) aur yeh inkar karte thay"
  68,44,"Pas aey Nabi, tum is kalam ke jhutlane walon ka maamla mujhpar chodh do hum aise tarike se inko batadreej tabahi ki taraf le jayenge ke inko khabar bhi na hogi"
  68,45,"Main inki rassi daraaz kar raha hoon, meri chaal badi zabardast hai"
  68,46,Kya tum insey koi ajar (compensation) talab kar rahey ho ke yeh is chatti ke bojh (feel burdened with debt) taley dabey ja rahe hoon
  68,47,Kya inke paas gaib ka ilam hai jisey yeh likh rahey hon
  68,48,"Pas apne Rubb ka faisla saadir honay tak sabr karo aur machli wale (younis) ki tarah na ho jao, jab usne pukara tha aur woh gham se bhara hua tha"
  68,49,Agar uske Rubb ki meharbani uske shamil-e-haal na ho jati to woh mazmoom (disgrace) hokar chatyal maidan mein phenk diya jata
  68,50,Aakhir-e-kaar uske Rubb ne usey barguzida (exalted) farma liya aur usey saleh bandon mein shamil kardiya
  68,51,"Jab yeh kafir log kalam-e-nasihat (Quran) sunte hain to tumhein aisi nazaron se dekhte hain ke goya tumhare qadam ukhaad denge, Aur kehte hain ke yeh zaroor deewana hai"
  68,52,Halaanke yeh to sarey jahaan walon ke liye ek naseehat hai
  69,1,"Honi shudhni ! (indubitable) [sach-much honay wali]"
  69,2,Kya hai woh honi shudni (indubitable)
  69,3,Aur tum kya jaano ke woh kya hai honi shudhni (indubitable)
  69,4,Samood aur Aad ne us achanak toot padne wali aafat ko jhutlaya
  69,5,To Samood ek sakht haadse mein halaaq kiye gaye
  69,6,Aur Aad ek badi shadeed toofani aandhi(storm) se tabah kardiye gaye
  69,7,Allah taala ne usko musalsal saat (seven) raat aur aath (eight) din unpar musallat rakkha (tum wahan hotey to) dekhte ke woh wahan is tarah pachade paday jaise woh khajoor ke boseeda (rotten) taney (trunks) hon
  69,8,Ab kya unmein se koi tumhein baki nazar aata hai
  69,9,Aur isi khata-e-azeem ka irtiqaab Firoun aur ussey pehle ke logon ne aur talpat (overturned) ho janey wali bastiyon ne kiya
  69,10,Un sab ne apne Rubb ke Rasool ki baat na maani to usne unko bade sakhti ke saath pakda
  69,11,Jab pani ka toofan hadd se guzar gaya to humne tumko kashti mein sawar kardiya tha
  69,12,Taa-ke is waqiye ko tumhare liye ek sabaq-aamoz yaadgaar bana dein aur yaad rakhne waley kaan iski yaad mehfooz rakkhein
  69,13,Phir jab ek dafa sur mein phoonk maar di jayegi
  69,14,Aur zameen aur pahadon ko utha kar ek hi chot mein reza reza kardiya jayega
  69,15,Us roz woh honay wala waqiya pesh aa jayega
  69,16,Usdin Aasmaan phatega aur uski bandish dhili padh jayegi
  69,17,Farishtey uske atraf-o-jawanib mein hongey aur aat (eight) farishtey us roz tere Rubb ka arsh apne upar uthaye huey hongey
  69,18,"Woh din hoga jab tumlog pesh kiye jaogey, tumhara koi raaz bhi chupa na reh jayega"
  69,19,"Us waqt jiska naam-e-aamal uske seedhey haath mein diya jayega woh kahega “lo dekho, padho mera naam-e-aamal"
  69,20,Main samajhta tha ke mujhey zaroor apna hisaab milne wala hai”
  69,21,Pas woh dil pasand aish mein hoga
  69,22,Aali muqaam jannat mein
  69,23,Jiske phalon ke guchhey jhuke padh rahey hongey
  69,24,(Aise logon se kaha jayega) mazey se khao aur pio apne un aamal ke badle jo tumne guzre huey dino mein kiye hain
  69,25,Aur jiska naam-e-aamal uske bayein (left) haath mein diya jayega woh kahega “ kaash mera aamal nama mujhey na diya gaya hota
  69,26,Aur main na jaanta ke mera hisaab kya hai
  69,27,Kaash meri wahi maut (jo duniya mei aayi thi) faisla-kun hoti
  69,28,Aaj mera maal mere kuch kaam na aaya
  69,29,Mera sara iqtedaar khatam ho gaya
  69,30,(hukum hoga) pakdo isey aur iski gardan mei touk daal do
  69,31,Phir isey jahannum mein jhoonk do
  69,32,Phir isko satter(seventy) haath lambi zanjeer mei jakad do
  69,33,Yeh na Allah buzurg-o-bartar par iman lata tha
  69,34,Aur na miskeen ko khana khilane ki targeeb deta tha
  69,35,Lihaza aaj na yahan iska koi yaar-e-gamkhaar hai
  69,36,Aur na zakhmon ke dhowan (washing of wounds) ke siwa iske liye koi khana
  69,37,Jisey khatakaaron (sinners) ke siwa koi nahin khata
  69,38,"Pas nahin, main qasam khata hoon un cheezon ki bhi jo tum dekhte ho"
  69,39,Aur unki bhi jinhein tum nahin dekhte
  69,40,Yeh ek Rasool-e-kareem ka qaul ( speech ) hai
  69,41,"Kisi shayar ka qaul nahin hai, tumlog kam hi iman latey ho"
  69,42,"Aur na yeh kisi kaahin(soothsayer) ka qaul hai , tum log kam hi gaur karte ho"
  69,43,Yeh Rabb-ul alameen ki taraf se nazil huwa hai
  69,44,Aur agar is (Nabi) ne khud ghad kar koi baat hamari taraf mansook ki hoti
  69,45,To hum iska dayan(right) haath padkad letay
  69,46,Aur iski rag-e-gardan (life vein) kaat daalte
  69,47,Phir tum mein se koi (humein)is kaam se rokne wala na hota
  69,48,Dar haqeeqat yeh parheizgar logon ke liye ek naseehat hai
  69,49,Aur hum jante hain ke tum mein se kuch log jhutlane waley hain
  69,50,Aise kafiron ke liye yaqeenan yeh mujeeb-e-hasrat (cause of regret) hai
  69,51,Aur yeh bilkul yaqeeni haqq hai
  69,52,"Pas aey nabi, apne Rubb-e-azeem ke naam ki tasbeeh karo"
  70,1,Mangne waley ne azaab maanga hai (woh azaab) jo zaroor waqey honay wala hai
  70,2,"Kafiron ke liye hai, koi usey dafa karne wala nahin"
  70,3,Us khuda ki taraf se hai jo urooj ke zeeno (ascending steps)ka malik hai
  70,4,Malaika (angels) aur rooh(Jibrael) uske huzoor chadh kar jatey hain ek aise din mein jiski miqdar pacchas (fifty) hazar saal hai
  70,5,"Pas aey Nabi, sabr karo, shaista sabr"
  70,6,Yeh log usey dur samajhte hain
  70,7,Aur hum usey qareeb dekh rahey hain
  70,8,(woh azaab us roz hoga) jis roz aasman pigli huye chandi ki tarah ho jayega
  70,9,Aur pahad rang-bi-rang ke dhunke huey oon (wool) jaise ho jayenge
  70,10,Aur koi jigri dost apne jigri dost ko na puchega
  70,11,"Halaanke woh ek dusre ko dikhaye jayenge, mujrim chahega ke us din ke azaab se bachne ke liye apni aulad ko"
  70,12,"Apni biwi ko, apne bhai ko"
  70,13,Apne qareeb-tareen khandaan ko jo usey panaah dene wala tha
  70,14,Aur rooh-e-zameen ke sab logon ko fidiya (badle) mein dey-de aur yeh tadbeer usey nijaat dila de
  70,15,Hargiz nahin woh to bhadakti hui aag ki lapat hogi
  70,16,Jo gosht posht ko chaat jayegi
  70,17,Pukar pukar kar apni taraf bulayegi har us shaks ko jisne haqq se mooh moda aur peet pheri
  70,18,Aur maal jamaa kiya aur seint seint kar (amassed wealth) rakkha
  70,19,Insan thud-dila (impatient) paida kiya gaya hai
  70,20,Jab uspar museebat aati hai to ghabra uthta hai
  70,21,Aur jab usey khush-haali naseeb hoti hai to bukhl (kanjoosi) karne lagta hai
  70,22,Magar woh log (is aib se bache huey hai) jo namaz padne waley hain
  70,23,Jo apni namaz ki hamesha pabandi karte hai
  70,24,Jinke maalon mein
  70,25,Saahil (maangne waley) aur mehroom ka ek haqq mukarrar hai
  70,26,Jo roz-e-jaza ko barhaq maante hain
  70,27,Jo apne Rubb ke azaab se darte hain
  70,28,Kyunke unke Rubb ka azaab aisi cheez nahin hai jissey koi bekhauf ho
  70,29,Jo apni sharmgahon ki hifazat karte hain
  70,30,Ba-juz apne biwiyon ya apni mamluka aurton ke jinse mehfooz na rakhne mein unpar koi malamat nahin
  70,31,Albatta jo iske alawa kuch aur chahein wahi hadd se tajawuz karne wala hai
  70,32,Jo apne amanaton ki hifazat aur apne ahad (covenant) ka paas karte hai
  70,33,Jo apni gawahiyon mein raast baazi (upright) par qayam rehte hain
  70,34,Aur jo apni namaz ki hifazat karte hain
  70,35,Yeh log izzat ke saath jannat ke baaghon mei rahenge
  70,36,"Pas aey Nabi , kya baat hai ke yeh munkirin dayein(left) aur bayein(right) se"
  70,37,Giroh (crowds) dar giroh(crowds) tumhari taraf daude chale aa rahe hain
  70,38,Kya inmein se har ek yeh lalaj rakhta hai ke woh niyamat bhari jannat mein daakhil kardiya jayega
  70,39,Hargiz nahin humne jis cheez se inko paida kiya hai usey yeh khud jaante hain
  70,40,"Pas nahin, main qasam khata hoon mashrikon aur maghribon ke maalik ki hum ispar qadir hain"
  70,41,Ke inki jagah insey behtar log le aayein aur koi humse baazi le jaane wala nahin hai
  70,42,Lihaza inhein apni behuda baaton aur apne khel mein pada rehne do yahan tak ke yeh apne us din ko pahunch jayenge jiska insey waada kiya ja raha hai
  70,43,Jab yeh apni qabron se nikal kar is tarah daude ja rahey hongey jaise apne buthon (idols) ke aasthano (altars) ki taraf daud rahey hon
  70,44,"Inki nigahein jhuki hui hongi, zillat inpar chaa rahi hogi, woh din hai jiska insey wada kiya ja raha hai"
  71,1,Humne Nooh ko uski qaum ki taraf bheja (is hidayat ke saath) ke apni qaum ke logon ko khabardar karde qabl iske ke unpar ek dardnaak azaab aaye
  71,2,"Usne kaha “ Aey meri qaum ke logon, main tumhare liye ek saaf saaf khabardar kardene wala (paighambar) hoon"
  71,3,(Tumko aagah karta hoon) ke Allah ki bandagi karo aur ussey daro aur meri itaat (follow) karo
  71,4,Allah tumhare gunaahon se darguzar farmayega aur tumhein ek waqt-e-mukarrar tak baaki rakkhega. Haqeeqat yeh hai ke Allah ka mukarrar kiya hua waqt jab aa jata hai to phir taala nahin jata kaash tumhein iska ilm ho
  71,5,"Usne arz kiya “Aey mere Rubb , maine apni qaum ke logon ko shab-o-roz (night and day) pukara"
  71,6,Magar meri pukar ne unke farar hi mei izafa kiya
  71,7,"Aur jab bhi maine unko bulaya taa-ke tu unhein maaf karde , unhon ne kaano mein ungliyan thoos li aur apne kapdon se mooh dhaank liye aur apni rawish par adh gaye aur bada takabbur (proudness) kiya"
  71,8,Phir maine unko haanke pukarey (openly) ki dawat di
  71,9,Phir maine aelaniya (publicly) bhi unko tableeg ki aur chupke chupke bhi samjhaya
  71,10,"Maine kaha apne Rubb se maafi maango,beshak woh bada maaf karne wala hai"
  71,11,Woh tumpar aasmaan se khoob baarishein barsayega
  71,12,"Tumhein maal aur aulad se nawaze ga, tumhare liye baagh paida karega aur tumhare liye nehrein jaari kardega"
  71,13,Tumhein kya ho gaya hai ke Allah ke liye tum kisi waqar (majesty) ki tawakku nahin rakhte
  71,14,Halaanke usne tarah tarah se tumhein banaya hai
  71,15,Kya dekhte nahin ho ke Allah ne kis tarah saat aasman teh-bar-teh banaye
  71,16,Aur unmein chand ko noor aur suraj ko chiraag banaya
  71,17,Aur Allah ne tumko zameen se ajeeb tarah ugaya
  71,18,Phir woh tumhein isi zameen mein wapas le jayega aur issey yakayak tumko nikal khada karega
  71,19,Aur Allah ne zameen ko tumhare liye farsh ki tarah bicha diya
  71,20,Taa-ke tum uske andar khule raaston mein chalo
  71,21,"Nooh ne kaha “mere Rubb, unhon ne meri baat radd kardi aur un (raheeson) ki pairvi ki jo maal aur aulad paa kar aur zyada na murad ho gaye hain"
  71,22,In logon ne bada bhaari makr (plot) ka jaal phaila rakkha hai
  71,23,"Inhon ne kaha hargiz na chodo apne maboodon (deities) ko, aur na chodo Wadd aur Suwa ko aur na Yagus aur Yaook aur Nasr ko (idol names)"
  71,24,"Inhon ne bahut logon ko gumraah kiya hai, aur tu bhi in zalimon ko gumrahi ke siwa kisi cheez mein tarakki na de"
  71,25,"Apni khataon ki bina par hi woh garq(drown) kiye gaye aur Aag mein jhoonk diye gaye , phir unhon ne apne liye Allah se bachane wala koi madadgar na paya"
  71,26,"Aur Nooh ne kaha “Mere Rubb, In kafiron mein se koi zameen par basne wala na chodh"
  71,27,Agar tu ne inko chodh diya to yeh tere bandon ko gumraah karenge aur inki nasal se jo bhi paida hoga badkar aur sakht kafir hi hoga
  71,28,"Mere Rubb, mujhey aur mere waldain ko aur har us shaks ko jo mere ghar mein momin ki haisiyat se dakhil hua hai, Aur sab momin mardon aur auraton ko maaf farma de, Aur zalimon ke liye halakat ke siwa kisi cheez mein izafa na kar"
  72,1,"Aey Nabi, kaho, meri taraf wahee (revelation) bheji gayi hai ke Jinno ke ek giroh (group) ne gaur se suna phir (jaa kar apne qaum ke logon se) kaha: “humne ek bada hi ajeeb Quran suna hai"
  72,2,Jo raah-e-raast ki taraf rehnumayi karta hai is liye hum uspar iman le aaye hain aur ab hum hargiz apne Rubb ke saath kisi ko sharik nahin karenge
  72,3,"Aur yeh ke hamare Rubb ki shaan bahut aala-o-Arfa hai , usne kisi ko biwi ya beta nahin banaya"
  72,4,Aur yeh ke hamare nadaan log Allah ke barey mein bahut khilaf-e-haqq baatein karte rahey hain
  72,5,Aur yeh ke humne samjha tha ke insaan aur jinn kabhi khuda ke baarey mein jhoot nahin bol sakte
  72,6,"Aur yeh ke Insano mein se kuch log Jinno mein se kuch logon ki panaah (refuge) maanga karte thay, is tarah unhon ne Jinno ka guroor aur zyada badha diya"
  72,7,Aur yeh ke insaano ne bhi wahi gumaan kiya jaisa tumhara gumaan tha ke Allah kisi ko Rasool bana kar na bhejega
  72,8,Aur yeh ke humne aasman ko tatola to dekha ke woh pehray-daaron (terrible guards) se patha pada hai aur shahabon (shooting meteors) ki baarish ho rahi hai
  72,9,"Aur yeh ke pehle hum sun-gun lene ke liye aasman mei baithnay ki jagah paa lete thay, magar ab jo chori chupey sunne ke koshish karta hai woh apne liye ghaat mein ek shahabe saaqib (shooting meteors) laga hua paata hai"
  72,10,Aur yeh ke hamari samajh mein na aata tha ke aaya zameen walon ke saath koi bura maamla karne ka irada kiya gaya hai ya unka Rubb unhein raah-e-raast dikhana chahta hai
  72,11,"Aur yeh ke hum mein se kuch log saleh (upright) hain aur kuch is se farotar hain, hum mukhtalif tareeqon (ways/factions) mein batey (divided) huey hain"
  72,12,Auy yeh ke hum samajhte thay ke na zameen mein hum Allah ko aajiz (frustrate) kar sakte hain aur na bhaag kar usey hara saktey hain
  72,13,Aur yeh ke humne jab hidayat ki taleem suni to hum uspar iman le aaye ab jo koi bhi apne Rubb par iman le aayega usey kisi haq-talfi ya zulm ka khauff na hoga
  72,14,Aur yeh ke hum mein se kuch muslim(Allah ke itaat guzar) hain aur kuch haqq se munharif (upright) to jinhon ne Islam (itaat ka raasta) ikhtiyar kar liya unhon ne najaat ki raah dhoond li
  72,15,Aur jo haqq se muhnarif hai woh jahannum ka indhan (fuel) banney wala hai
  72,16,Aur (aey Nabi kaho mujhpar yeh wahee bhi ki gayi hai ke) log agar raah-e-raast par sabit qadami (firmly) se chalte to hum unhein khoob sairaab karte (provide abundant rain)
  72,17,Taa-ke is niyamat se unki aazmaish karein aur jo apne Rubb ke zikr se mooh modega uska Rubb usey sakht azaab mein mubtala kardega
  72,18,"Aur yeh ke masjidein Allah ke liye hai, lihaza unmein Allah ke saath kisi aur ko na pukaro"
  72,19,Aur yeh ke jab Allah ka banda usko pukarne ke liye khada hua to log uspar toot padne ke liye tayyar ho gaye
  72,20,"Aey Nabi ,kaho ke main to apne Rubb ko pukarta hoon aur uske saath kisi ko sharik nahin karta"
  72,21,Kaho main tum logon keliye na kisi nuksan ka ikhtiyar rakhta hoon na kisi bhalayi ka
  72,22,Kaho mujhey Allah ki giraft se koi nahin bacha sakta aur na main uske daaman ke siwa koi jaye panaah (refuge) paa sakta hoon
  72,23,Mera kaam iske siwa kuch nahin hai ke Allah ki baat aur uske paighamaat pahuncha doon. Ab jo bhi Allah aur uske Rasool ki baat na maanega uske liye jahannum ki aag hai aur aisey log usmein hamesha rahenge
  72,24,(Yeh log apni is rawish se baaz na aayenge) yahan tak ke jab us cheez ko dekh lenge jiska inse waada kiya ja raha hai to inhein maloom ho jayega ke kiske madadgaar kamzoar hain aur kiska jattha (group) taadad mein kam hai
  72,25,"Kaho, main nahin jaanta ke jis cheez ka waada tumse kiya ja raha hai woh qareeb hai ya mera Rubb uske liye koi lambi muddat muqarrar famata hai"
  72,26,"Woh aalimul gaib hai , apne gaib par kisi ko muttala (reveal/disclose) nahin karta"
  72,27,"Siwai us Rasool ke jisey usne (gaib ka koi ilm dene ke liye) pasand karliya ho, to uske aagey aur pichey woh muhafiz (guards) laga deta hai"
  72,28,"Taa-ke woh jaan le ke unhon ne apne Rubb ke paighamaat pahuncha diye, aur woh unke poorey maahol ka ihata (encompass) kiye huey hai aur ek ek cheez ko usne gin rakkha hai"
  73,1,Aey oad lapet kar (enwrapped ) sone waley
  73,2,Raat ko namaz mein khade raha karo magar kam
  73,3,Aadhi Raat
  73,4,"Ya issey kuch kam karlo ya issey kuch zyada badha do, aur Quran ko khoob tehar tehar kar padho"
  73,5,Hum tumpar ek bhari kalam nazil karne waley hain
  73,6,Dar haqeeqat raat ka uthna nafs par qaabu paney ke liye bahut kaargar aur Quran theek padhne ke liye zyada mauzu (suitable) hai
  73,7,Din ke auqat mein to tumhare liye bahut masrufiyat (prolonged occupation) hai
  73,8,Apne Rubb ke naam ka zikr kiya karo aur sabse katt kar usi ke ho raho
  73,9,"Woo mashrik (east) o magrib (west) ka maalik hai, uske siwa koi khuda nahin hai, lihaza usi ko apna wakeel bana lo"
  73,10,Aur jo baatein log bana rahey hain unpar sabr karo aur sharafat ke saath unse alag ho jao
  73,11,In jhutlane waley khush haal logon se nimatne ka kaam tum mujhpar chodh do aur inhein zara kuch dair isi halat par rehne do
  73,12,Hamarey paas (inke liye) bhaari bediyan hain aur bhadakti hui aag
  73,13,Aur halaq(throat) mein phasne wala khana aur dard-naak azaab
  73,14,Yeh us din hoga jab zameen aur pahad laraz uthengey aur pahadon ka haal aisa ho jaeyga jaise reit (sand) ke dhair hai jo bhikhre ja rahe hain
  73,15,Tum logon ke paas humne usi tarah ek rasool tum par gawah bana kar bheja hai jis tarah humne Firaun ki taraf ek rasool bheja tha
  73,16,(Phir dekhlo ke jab ) Firaun ne us Rasool ki baat na maani to humne usko badi sakhti kay saath pakad liya
  73,17,Agar tum maan-ne se inkar karoge to us din kaisey bach jaogey jo bacchon ko boodha kardega
  73,18,Aur jiski sakhti se aasman phata ja raha hoga?Allah ka wada to poora hokar hi rehna hai
  73,19,"Yeh ek nasihat hai , ab jiska jee chahey apne Rubb ki taraf janey ka rasta ikhtiyar karle"
  73,20,"Aey Nabi, tumhara Rubb janta hai ke tum kabhi do tihayi (two-third) raat ke qareeb aur kabhi aadhi raat aur kabhi ek tihayi (one-third) raat ibadat mein khade rehtey ho,Aur tumhare saathiyon mein se bhi ek giroh yeh amal karta hai, Allah hi raat aur din ke auqat ka hisab rakhta hai. Usey maloom hai ke tumlog auqat ka theek shumar nahin kar sakte, lihaza usne tumpar meharbani farmayi, Ab jitna Quran aasani se padh sakte ho padh liya karo. Usey maloom hai ke tum mein kuch mareez hongey, kuch dusre log Allah ke fazal(bounty) ki talash mein safar karte hain, Aur kuch aur log Allah ki raah mein jung karte hain, pas jitna Quran ba aasani padha ja sakey padh liya karo, namaz qayam karo, zakaat do aur Allah ko accha qarz dete raho, jo kuch bhalayi tum apne liye aagey bhejoge usey Allah ke yahan maujood paogey, wahi zyada behtar hai aur uska ajr bahut bada hai. Allah se magfirat maangte raho, beshak Allah bada Gafoor o Raheem hai"
  74,1,Aey oad lapeit (enveloped) kar laitney waley
  74,2,Utho aur khabardar karo
  74,3,Aur apne Rubb ki badayi ka elan karo
  74,4,Aur apne kapde paak rakho
  74,5,Aur gandagi se dur raho
  74,6,Aur ehsan na karo zyada hasil karne keliye
  74,7,Aur apne Rubb ki khatir sabr karo
  74,8,Accha jab soor mein phook maari jayegi
  74,9,Woh din bada hi sakht din hoga
  74,10,Kafiron ke liye halka na hoga
  74,11,Chodh do mujhey aur us shaks ko jisey maine akela paida kiya hai
  74,12,Bahut sa maal usko diya
  74,13,Uske saath hazir rehne waley bete diye
  74,14,Aur uske liye riyasat ki raah hamwaar ki
  74,15,Phir woh tama (greedily desire) rakhta hai ke main usey aur zyada doon
  74,16,Hargiz nahin woh hamari ayaat se inaath(stubbornly oppose) rakhta hai
  74,17,Main to usey ankareeb ek kathin chadhai chadwaunga
  74,18,Usne socha aur kuch baat banane ki koshish ki
  74,19,"To khuda ki maar uspar, kaisi baat banane ki koshish ki"
  74,20,"Haan, khuda ki maar uspar , kaisi baat banane ki koshish ki"
  74,21,Phir(logon ki taraf) dekha
  74,22,Phir peshani sukedi aur mooh banaya
  74,23,Phir palta aur takabbur mein padh gaya
  74,24,Aakhir e kaar bola ke yeh kuch nahin hai magar ek jaadu jo pehle se chala aa raha hai
  74,25,Yeh to ek Insani kalaam hai
  74,26,Anqareeb main usey dozakh mei jhonk dunga
  74,27,Aur tum kya jaano ke kya hai woh dozakh
  74,28,Na baqi rakhey na chodey
  74,29,Khaal(skin) jhulas dene wali
  74,30,Unnis (ninteen) karkoon uspar muqarrar hain
  74,31,"Humne dozakh ke yeh karkoon farishtey banaye hain,aur unki tadaad ko kafiron ke liye fitna bana diya hai, taa-ke ehle kitaab ko yaqeen aa jaye aur iman laney walon ka iman badhey,Aur ehle kitaab aur momineen kisi shakk mein na rahey,aur dil ke bimar aur kuffar yeh kahein ke bhala Allah ka is ajeeb baat se kya matlab ho sakta hai. Is tarah Allah jisey chahta hai gumraah kardeta hai aur jisey chahta hai hidayat baksh deta hai aur tere Rubb ke lashkaron (soldiers) ko khud uske siwa koi nahin janta, aur is dozak ka zikr iske siwa kisi garz ke liye nahin kiya gaya hai ke logon ko issey naseehat ho"
  74,32,"Hargiz nahin,kasam hai Chand ki"
  74,33,Aur Raat ki jabke woh palat-ti hai
  74,34,Aur subah ki jabke woh roshan hoti hai
  74,35,Yeh dozakh bhi badi cheezon mein se ek hai
  74,36,Insano ke liye darawa
  74,37,Tum mein se har us shaks ke liye darawa jo aagey badhna chahey ya pichey reh jana chahey
  74,38,"Har mutanaffis, apne kasb ke badle rehan hai (hostage to one’s deeds)"
  74,39,Dayein bazu walon ke siwa
  74,40,"Jo jannaton mein hongey, wahan woh"
  74,41,Mujrimon se puchenge
  74,42,Tumhein kya cheez dozakh mein le gayi
  74,43,woh kahenge “hum namaz padne walon mein se na thay
  74,44,Aur miskeen ko khana nahin khilate thay
  74,45,Aur haqq ke khilaf batein banane walon ke saath milkar hum bhi batein banane lagte thay
  74,46,Aur roz-e-jaza ko jhoot karar dete thay
  74,47,Yahan tak ke humein us yaqeeni cheez se saabqa pesh aa gaya”
  74,48,Us waqt sifarish karne walon ki sifarish unke kisi kaam na ayegi
  74,49,Aakhir in logon ko kya ho gaya hai ke yeh is nasihat se mooh moad rahey hain
  74,50,Goya yeh jungli gadhey hain
  74,51,Jo Sher se darr kar bhaag padey hain
  74,52,Balke inmein se to har ek yeh chahta hai ke uske naam khule khat (scroll/scripture) bhejey jaye
  74,53,"Hargiz nahin, Asal baat yeh hai ke yeh aakhirat ka khauf nahin rakhtey"
  74,54,"Hargiz nahin,yeh to ek nasihat hai"
  74,55,Ab jiska jee chahey issey sabaq hasil karle
  74,56,Aur yeh koi sabaq hasil na karengey illa yeh ke Allah hi aisa chahey woh iska haqdar hai ke ussey taqwa kiya jaye aur woh iska ehal hai ke (taqwa karne walon ko) baksh de
  75,1,Nahin main kasam khata hoon qayamat ke din ki
  75,2,"Aur nahin,main kasam khata hoon malamat karne wale nafs ki"
  75,3,Kya Insan yeh samajh raha hai ke hum uski haddiyon ko jama na kar sakengey
  75,4,Kyun nahin? Hum to uski ungliyon ke por por tak theek bana dene par qadir hain
  75,5,Magar Insan chahta yeh hai ke aagey bhi badh-aamaliyan karta rahey
  75,6,“Puchta hai” aakhir kab aana hai woh qayamat ka din
  75,7,Phir jab dedhey pathra jayengey (sight is dazed)
  75,8,Aur chand be-noor ho jayega
  75,9,Aur Chand Suraj mila kar ek kardiya jayenge
  75,10,Us waqt yahi Insan kahega kahan bhaag kar jaun
  75,11,"Hargiz nahin,wahan koi jaye panaah na hogi"
  75,12,Us roz terey Rubb hi ke samney jaakar theharna hoga
  75,13,Us roz Insan ko uska sab agla pichla kiya karaya bata diya jayega
  75,14,Balke Insan khud hi apne aap ko khoob janta hai
  75,15,Chahey woh kitni hi maazratein (excuses) karey
  75,16,"Aey Nabi , Is wahi ko jaldi jaldi yaad karne ke liye apni zubaan ko harkat na do"
  75,17,Isko yaad kara dena aur padhwa dena hamare zimmey hai
  75,18,Lihaza jab hum isey padh rahey hon us waqt tum iske qirat ko gaur se sunte raho
  75,19,Phir iska matlab samjha dena bhi hamarey zimmey hai
  75,20,"Hargiz nahin, asal baat yeh hai ke tum log jaldi haasil honay wali cheez (yani duniya) se muhabbat rakhte ho"
  75,21,Aur aakhirat ko chodh dete ho
  75,22,Us roz kuch chehrey tar-o-taza hongey
  75,23,Apne Rubb ki taraf dekh rahey hongey
  75,24,Aur kuch chehrey udas hongey
  75,25,Aur samajh rahey hongey ke unke saath qamar-todh bartao hone wala hai
  75,26,"Hargiz nahin, jab jaan halaq tak pahunch jayegi"
  75,27,Aur kaha jayega ke hai koi jhaad phook karne wala
  75,28,Aur aadmi samajh lega ke yeh duniya se judai ka waqt hai
  75,29,Aur pindli(leg) se pindli(leg) judh jayegi
  75,30,Woh din hoga tere Rubb ki taraf rawangi ka
  75,31,"Magar usne na sach mana , aur na namaz padhi"
  75,32,Balke jhutlaya aur palat gaya
  75,33,Phir akadta hua apne ghar walon ki taraf chal diya
  75,34,Yeh rawish tere hi liye sazawaar hai aur tujh hi ko zeib deti hai
  75,35,Haan yeh rawish tere hi liye sazawaar hai aur tujh hi ko zeib deti hai
  75,36,"Kya Insan ne yeh samajh rakkha hai ke woh yunhi mohmal (left alone, unquestioned )chodh diya jayega"
  75,37,Kya woh ek hakeer pani ka nutfa (sperm from semen) na tha jo (raham –e-madar mei) tapkaya jata hai
  75,38,"Phir woh ek lothda(clot) bana, phir Allah ne uska jism banaya aur uske aazaa durust kiye"
  75,39,Phir ussey mard aur aurat ki do qismein banayi
  75,40,Kya woh ispar qadir nahin hai ke marne walon ko phir zinda karde
  76,1,Kya Insan par la mutanahi zamane ka ek waqt aisa bhi guzra hai jab woh koi qabil e zikr cheez na tha
  76,2,Humne Insan ko ek makhlut nutfey (intermingled sperm) se paida kiya taa-ke uska imtihaan lein aur is garz ke liye humne usey sunne aur dekhne wala banaya
  76,3,"Humne usey rasta dikha diya, khwa shukar karne wala baney ya kufr karne wala"
  76,4,Kufr karne walon ke liye humne zanjeerein aur tauq (fetters) aur bhadakti hui aag muhaiyya kar rakkhi hai
  76,5,Neik log (jannat mein) sharaab ke aisey sagar piyenge jinmein aabey kafoor ki aamezish (mixture) hogi
  76,6,Yeh ek behta chasma(spring) hoga jiske pani ke saath Allah ke bandey sharaab piyengey aur jahan chahengey ba-sahulat uski shakhein (nikal) lengey
  76,7,"Yeh woh log hongey jo (duniya mein) nazar poori karte hain, aur us din se darte hain jiski aafat har taraf phaili hui hogi"
  76,8,Aur Allah ki muhabbat mein miskeen aur yateem aur qaidi ko khana khilate hain
  76,9,"Aur unse kehte hain ke (hum tumhein sirf) Allah ki khatir khila rahey hain, hum tumse na koi badla chahte hain na shukriya"
  76,10,Humey to apne Rubb se us din ke azaab ka khauf lahiq hai jo sakht museebat ka intehayi taweel din hoga
  76,11,Pas Allah taala unhein us din ke sharr se bacha lega aur unhein taazgi aur suroor bakshega
  76,12,Aur unke sabr ke badle mein unhein jannat aur reshmi libas ata karega
  76,13,"Wahan woh unchey masnadon par takiye lagaye baithey hongey, na unhein dhoop ki garmi satayegi na jaadey ki thirr (bitter cold)"
  76,14,"Jannat ki chaaon unpar jhuki hui saaya kar rahi hogi,aur uske phal har waqt unke bas mein hongey(ke jis tarah chahey unhein todh lein)"
  76,15,Unke aagey chandi ke bartan aur sheshey ke pyale gardish karaye ja rahey hongey
  76,16,"Sheshey bhi woh jo chandi ki qisam ke hongey,aur unko (muntazmin-e-jannat nay)theek andazey ke mutabik bhara hoga"
  76,17,Unko wahan aisi sharaab ke jaam pilaye jayenge jis mein soont (ginger) ki aamezish hogi
  76,18,Yeh jannat ka ek chasma hoga jisey salsabil kaha jata hai
  76,19,Unki khidmat ke liye aisey ladke daudte phir rahey hongey jo hamesha ladke hi rahenge.Tum unhein dekho to samjho ke moti(pearls) hai jo bikhair diye gaye hain
  76,20,Wahan jidhar bhi tum nigah dalogey niyamatein hi niyamatein aur ek badi sultanat ka sar o saman tumhein nazar aayega
  76,21,"Unke upar bareek resham ke sabz libas aur atlas o deba ke kapde (rich brocade)hongey, unko chandi ke kangan pehnaye jayenge , aur unka Rubb unko nihayat pakeeza sharaab pilaeyga"
  76,22,Yeh hai tumhari jaza aur tumhari kaar-guzari qabil-e-qadr thehri hai
  76,23,"Aey Nabi, humne hi tumpar yeh Quran thoda thoda karke nazil kiya hai"
  76,24,"Lihaza tum apne Rubb ke hukum par sabr karo, aur in mein se kisi badh-amal ya munkir-e-haq ki baat na maano"
  76,25,Apne Rubb ka naam subh-o-shaam yaad karo
  76,26,"Raat ko bhi uske huzoor sajda raiz ho, Aur raat ke taveel auqat mein uski tasbeeh karte raho"
  76,27,Yeh log to jaldi hasil honay wali cheez (duniya ) se muhabbat rakhte hai aur aagey jo bhaari din aane wala hai usey nazar andaz kardetey hain
  76,28,"Humne hi inko paida kiya hai aur inke jodh bandh mazboot kiye hai, aur hum jab chahein inki shakalon ko badal kar rakh dein"
  76,29,"Yeh ek nasihat hai,ab jiska jee chahey apne Rubb ki taraf jaane ka rasta ikhtiyar karle"
  76,30,"Aur tumharey chahne se kuch nahin hota jab tak ke Allah na chachey, yaqeenan Allah bada Aleem-o-Haqeem hai"
  76,31,"Apni rehmat mein jisko chahta hai daakhil karta hai, Aur zalimon ke liye usne dardnaak azaab tayyar kar rakkha hai"
  77,1,Kasam hai un ( hawaon) ki jo pai dar pai bheji jati hain
  77,2,Phir toofani raftar se chalti hai
  77,3,Aur (baadalon ko) utha kar phailati hai
  77,4,Phir (unko) phaad kar juda karti hai
  77,5,Phir (dilon mei khuda ki)yaad daalti hai
  77,6,Uzar (justification) ke taur par ya daravey ke taur par
  77,7,Jis cheez ka tumse wada kiya ja raha hai woh zaroor waqey honay wali hai
  77,8,Phir jab sitarey maand (extinguish) pad jayengey
  77,9,Aur aasmaan phaad diya jayega
  77,10,Aur pahad dhunak daaley jayengey (blown away)
  77,11,Aur Rasoolon ki haziri ka waqt aa pahunchega (us roz woh cheez waqey ho jaeygi)
  77,12,Kis roz ke liye yeh kaam utha rakha gaya hai
  77,13,Faisley ke roz ke liye
  77,14,Aur tumhein kya khabar ke woh faisley ka din kya hai
  77,15,Tabahi hai us din jhutlane walon ke liye
  77,16,Kya humne aglon ko halaq nahin kiya
  77,17,Phir unhi ke pichey hum baad walon ko chalta karengey
  77,18,Mujrimo ke saath hum yahi kuch kiya karte hain
  77,19,Tabahi hai us din jhutlaney walon ke liye
  77,20,Kya humne ek hakeer pani se tumhein paida nahin kiya
  77,21,Aur ek mukarrara muddat tak
  77,22,Usey ek mehfooz jagah thehraye rakkha
  77,23,"To dekho , hum ispar qadir thay, pas hum bahut acchi qudrat rakhne waley hain"
  77,24,Tabahi hai us roz jhutlaney walon ke liye
  77,25,Kya humne zameen ko sameth kar rakhne wali nahin banaya
  77,26,Zindon ke liye bhi aur murdon ke liye bhi
  77,27,"Aur is mein buland-o-bala pahad jamaye, Aur tumhein meetha pani pilaya"
  77,28,Tabahi hai us roz jhutlaney walon ke liye
  77,29,Chalo ab usi cheez ki taraf jisey tum jhutlaya karte thay
  77,30,Chalo us saaye ki taraf jo teen shaakhon(columns) wala hai
  77,31,Na thandak pahunchane wala aur na aag ki lapat se bachane wala
  77,32,woh aag mahal (castles/fortress) jaisi badi badi chingariyan phenkegi
  77,33,(Jo uchalti hui yun mehsus hongi )goya ke woh zard ount (camel) hai
  77,34,Tabahi hai us roz jhutlaney walon ke liye
  77,35,Yeh woh din hai jismein wo na kuch bolengey
  77,36,Aur na unhein mauka diya jaeyga ke koi uzr(excuse) pesh karein
  77,37,Tabahi hai us din jhutlaney walon ke liye
  77,38,Yeh faisley ka din hai humne tumhein aur tumse pehle guzrey huey logon ko jamaa kardiya hai
  77,39,Ab agar koi chaal tum chal sakte ho to mere muqabley mein chal dekho
  77,40,Tabahi hai us din jhutlaney walon ke liye
  77,41,Muttaqi log aaj saayon aur chashmon mein hai
  77,42,Aur jo phal woh chahein (unke liye hazir hai)
  77,43,Khao aur piyo mazey se apne un aamal ke siley mein jo tum karte rahey ho
  77,44,Hum neik logon ko aisi hi jaza detay hain
  77,45,Tabahi hai us roz jhutlaney walon ke liye
  77,46,"Kha lo aur mazey karlo thodey din, haqeeqat mein tum log mujrim ho"
  77,47,Tabahi hai us roz jhutlaney walon ke liye
  77,48,Jab inse kaha jata hai ke (Allah ke aagey) jhuko to nahin jhuktey
  77,49,Tabahi hai uss roz jhutlaney walon ke liye
  77,50,Ab is (Quran) ke baad aur kaunsa kalaam aisa ho sakta hai jispar yeh iman layein